v1

This is a fork of [nixbuild/nix-quick-install-action@v30](https://github.com/nixbuild/nix-quick-install-action/tree/v30).
Changes listed here are relative to that release.

## Changes
- Add support for Lix
  - Supported versions: 2.92.0, 2.91.1, 2.90.0
- Add `nix-implementation` option to allow selecting which Nix implementation to install
  - Supported implementations: nix, lix
- Change default version and implementation to Lix 2.92.0